                     <interp inst="t18680608-562-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="robbery"></interp>. Feloniously assaulting <persName id="t18680608-name-394" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18680608-name-394" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
